Outputs debugging information about the parser, not really intended for end-users.

## PARSE\_SYSLOG\_LINE\_QUIET

Disables warnings in the parse\_syslog\_line() function

## TEST\_ACTIVE / TEST2\_ACTIVE

Disables warnings in the parse\_syslog\_line() function

